OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary has pledged to save
OL,7,Fthe asylum system "for generations to
OL,8,Fcome" as she announced the opening of
OL,9,Fnew safe routes for refugees from the
OL,10,Fautumn.
OL,12,FBut plans announced by Shabana Mahmood
OL,13,Fon Friday night will also see changes
OL,14,Fto human rights laws that will make it
OL,15,Feasier to deport people who are in the
OL,16,Fcountry illegally.
OL,18,FMs Mahmood said: "I will open new
OL,19,Flegal routes for genuine refugees,
OL,20,Fwhile closing loopholes that have been
OL,21,Ftoo often abused.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,F"My goal is simple", she added, "to
OL,7,Fensure we have an asylum system not
OL,8,Fjust today, but for generations to
OL,9,Fcome."
OL,11,FThe new safe routes will allow
OL,12,Fcommunities and some "trusted"
OL,13,Funiversities to sponsor refugees to
OL,14,Fcome to the UK.
OL,16,FIt has been inspired by a Canadian
OL,17,Fscheme that has settled 400,000 people
OL,18,Fin the country since 1979.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FA separate route allowing employers to
OL,7,Fsponsor refugees is also expected to
OL,8,Fopen next year.
OL,10,FThe Home Office did not say how many
OL,11,Frefugees it expected to use the new
OL,12,Froutes, but it did say the system
OL,13,Fwould "operate at a much higher
OL,14,Fcapacity" than the current UK
OL,15,FResettlement Scheme that provides a
OL,16,Froute for only a small number of
OL,17,Fpeople each year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FIn addition to the new routes, Ms
OL,7,FMahmood has said a new Immigration and
OL,8,FAsylum Bill will seek to prevent
OL,9,F"abuse" of human rights laws,
OL,10,Fincluding the right to a family life
OL,11,Fand modern slavery protections.
OL,13,FThe new law will tighten the
OL,14,Fdefinition of "family" for the
OL,15,Fpurposes of the European Convention on
OL,16,FHuman Rights (ECHR), restricting it to
OL,17,Fimmediate family members only.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FCritics of the asylum system have
OL,7,Ffocused on Article 8 of the ECHR,
OL,8,Fsaying it has been used to frustrate
OL,9,Fthe deportation of people with no
OL,10,Fright to be in the UK.
OL,12,FThe Home Office said the new
OL,13,Fdefinition would prevent situations
OL,14,Fsuch as one that prevented the
OL,15,Fdeportation of a convicted domestic
OL,16,Fabuser from Poland because he acted as
OL,17,Fa "father figure" to his nephew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FThe new legislation will also remove
OL,7,Fmodern slavery protections from
OL,8,Fforeign offenders who have been jailed
OL,9,Fand reject claims made when
OL,10,Fdeportation action has already
OL,11,Fcommenced if there was an opportunity
OL,12,Fto make a claim earlier.
OL,14,FMs Mahmood said: "Britain has always
OL,15,Foffered sanctuary to those fleeing war
OL,16,Fand persecution.
OL,18,F"But this system only survives if the
OL,19,Fpublic trusts that it is fair,
OL,20,Fcontrolled, and not open to abuse."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
