PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBut Friday's announcement comes as Ms
OL,12,FMahmood faces questions about whether
OL,13,Fshe will remain in post once Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer leaves Downing Street.
OL,16,FHer planned changes to rules governing
OL,17,Findefinite leave to remain (ILR) have
OL,18,Fdrawn criticism from some Labour MPs,
OL,19,Fwith Sir Keir's likely successor Andy
OL,20,FBurnham facing calls to scrap them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782652704
OL,3,CMahmood announces plan to open safe
OL,4,Croutes for refugees
OL,6,FDuring his by-election campaign in
OL,7,FMakerfield, Mr Burnham suggested that
OL,8,Fhe wanted a "consultation" on the
OL,9,Fproposals, leaving open the
OL,10,Fpossibility that they could be revised.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood also spent Friday embroiled
OL,13,Fin a row with one of her junior
OL,14,Fministers, Mike Tapp, after he
OL,15,Fsuggested exempting care workers from
OL,16,Fher ILR reforms.
OL,18,FSir Keir resisted her calls to sack Mr
OL,19,FTapp, with Downing Street issuing a
OL,20,Frebuke to both ministers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
